description\" : \"Spring Boot AMQP provides auto-configuration and support classes for AMQP 1.0 messaging in Spring Boot applications. It configures ProtonJ2-backed connection factories, AMQP clients, Jackson message conversion, connection properties, Docker Compose integration, and Testcontainers connection details.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-amqp/index.json:37:    \"description\" : \"Spring Boot AMQP provides auto-configuration and support classes for integrating Spring Boot applications with AMQP messaging. It configures RabbitMQ-related infrastructure such as connection factories, templates, listener containers, health checks, metrics, Docker Compose support, and Testcontainers integration.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-jdbc/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Spring Boot JDBC provides auto-configuration and support classes for JDBC-based data access in Spring Boot applications. It configures data sources, JDBC templates, transaction managers, database initialization, health checks, connection pool metrics, and Docker Compose/Testcontainers connection details.\",\nmetadata/com.github.docker-java/docker-java-transport/3.2.13/reachability-metadata.json:5:        \"typeReached\": \"com.github.dockerjava.transport.UnixSocket\"\nmetadata/com.github.docker-java/docker-java-transport/index.json:5:    \"source-code-url\" : \"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/com/github/docker-java/docker-java-transport/$version$/docker-java-transport-$version$-sources.jar\",\nmetadata/com.github.docker-java/docker-java-transport/index.json:6:    \"repository-url\" : \"https://github.com/docker-java/docker-java\",\nmetadata/com.github.docker-java/docker-java-transport/index.json:7:    \"test-code-url\" : \"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/com/github/docker-java/docker-java-transport/$version$/docker-java-transport-$version$-tests.jar\",\nmetadata/com.github.docker-java/docker-java-transport/index.json:8:    \"documentation-url\" : \"https://repo1.ma